1.1.0 (2026-07-04)
- Split the app into scenes reducing memory usage.
- Release the map data from memory as soon as the selected track's walls are extracted, so only the active track is kept during a race.
- Add a roach sprite image (assets/ROACH.JSON) rotated so the head faces the direction of travel.
- Speeds are now named constants at the top of RACE.JS for easy tuning.
- Roach letter labels show beside the roaches during the countdown, on the side of the start lineup that faces the track center. 
- While the roaches are traveling the labels are hidden. Every few seconds it displays again.
- ROACH letters display again at the finish.

